claim.claim-text:
A method of controlling a plurality of light-emitting element array chips included in an image forming apparatus, the method comprising:
receiving print data;
applying a transfer signal operating a transfer element array;
applying a data signal operating a light-emitting element array; and
applying an additional signal operating a light-emitting element at a point in time when the transfer signal is changing from a high-level to a low-level.
